{"tid":1065452,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解搭地鐵過海都特別貴？","createTime":"2019-03-17T09:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:15:58.000Z","uid":97649,"like":728,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"9c21209744259c226eb1585c8c1fad63547ba9ef","tid":1065452,"uid":97649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設由將軍澳站出發，終點站分別係北角同尖沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n如果去北角，地鐵嘅建議路線緊係直接搭將軍澳線過海，搭四個站，預計車程就12分鐘，用八達通嘅話車費要$12.3。<br />\n<br />\n如果去尖沙嘴，地鐵app嘅建議路線係搭將軍澳過海去北角轉港島線去金鐘再轉荃灣線去尖沙嘴，一共搭10個站，過兩次海，預計車程就29分鐘，車費都只係$10.4。<br />\n<br />\n你話搭巴士每次過海要俾隧道費，所以貴啲都好合理。但係搭地鐵應該唔使俾隧道費啊？點解都要咁貴？<br />\n<br />\n路軌、過海隧道保養要錢我知，但係點解去尖沙嘴要過兩次海都仲平過去北角？<br />\n<br />\n路程問題？又唔會啊，去尖沙嘴路程一定遠過去北角啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解地鐵要食水咁深！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />車費好貴啊！！！"},{"pid":"6c2fc19e8074997c2404e28f107b50bacab3d7a1","tid":1065452,"uid":241924,"like":437,"dislike":3,"score":434,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"因為你係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96819c24292e62d0018c10a096b1f74cc3dcb8f","tid":1065452,"uid":97649,"like":187,"dislike":4,"score":183,"quote":{"pid":"6c2fc19e8074997c2404e28f107b50bacab3d7a1","tid":1065452,"uid":241924,"like":437,"dislike":3,"score":434,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"因為你係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"係一個窮嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n財政預算案完全無福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53e923e8dd8cebc3ab014416a64aa38b11a93cd","tid":1065452,"uid":159870,"like":176,"dislike":7,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"因為地鐵要過海最快"},{"pid":"c4d253fac4a21822df829473a221aa869081bc92","tid":1065452,"uid":512